content.rendered:
Directed by Suresh Triveni.

Written by Vijay Maurya. Vijay Maurya. Suresh Triveni.

Cast Vidya Balan(Sulochana / Sulu). Manav Kaul(Ashok). Neha Dhupia(Maria). Vijay Maurya(Pankaj). Malishka Mendonsa(RJ Albeli Anjali). Abhishek Sharrma(Pranav (as Abhishek Sharma)). Mahesh Pillai(School Principal). Sindhu Shekharan(Aradhana). Seema Taneja(Kalpana). Ajoy Chakraborty(Brother-in-law 1). Mandeep Kumar(Brother-in-law 2). Ayushmann Khurrana(Self (special appearance)). Santanu Ghatak(Sanjay / Music Composer). Trupti Khamkar(Lady Driver). Uday Lagoo(Sulu’s Father). Hitesh Dave(Lalji Bhai). Siddhaanth Samant(Chetan). Sonel Singh(Girija). Vibhawari Deshpande(Lady Police Officer Who gets Pranav home). Siven Sankaran Devendran(Tiffin Vendor). Bhumika Dube(Gym Receptionist). Nailah Qureshi(Jet Air Hostess 1). Charu Bhatt(Jet Air Hostess 2). Ajit Kelkar(Sudhakar Shetty). Raghu Sawhney(Mathuradas Brother 1). Vidhyadhar Karmakar(Mathuradas Brother 2). Latafat Shaikh(Lalji Bhai’s Assistant). Joslyn Braganza(Guitarist). Candy Fernandez(Race Participant 4). Tanuj Garg(Papad Client). Amit Gehani(Referee). Asha Joshi(Old Receptionist). 

Language Hindi.

Producers Vicky Bhatia. Swati Iyer Chawla. Hanif Chunawala. Deepika Gandhi. Tanuj Garg. Akshiti Goleria. Priya Gupta. Atul Kasbekar. Bhushan Kumar. Krishan Kumar. Shanti Sivaram Maini. Priyanka Mehta. Piya Sawhney.

Production Ellipsis Entertainment. T-Series.
